overview: A quiet campsite. Some of the campers here disappear. One day, the sisters come to the campsite to play. The owner, who cuts and eats raw, dripping meat, takes an interest in the sisters who are camping. The owner, Mansu, kindly takes care of the food separately and tells him to come home and use it comfortably instead of the messy public toilet. A sister who drank and fell asleep with the purpose of having fun, but when morning came, only her younger brother Eugene remained in the tent, and her older sister Yeong-ok disappeared. Young-ok, who is captured and imprisoned by the owner, eats only raw meat without missing a single meal, and her brother Eugene, who is left alone, begins to tremble in fear.
title: Sister Raising: What Happened at Camping
